  "description": "A refreshed classic look for all things wooden.",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/tuFZjG9UHU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/894050782004006962/1115108842422947941/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"455\" height=\"105\" /><br /></a></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/894050782004006962/1115100882619617331/cover.png\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'trebuchet ms', geneva, sans-serif;\">About</span></strong></span></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>bogie's Trees and Timber</strong> overhauls most of the basic wood blocks in the game to have a refreshed classic look and some new features. I plan on updating this pack in the future with more stuff.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">1.0.0 Currently adds:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">All planks</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Vertical planks (double slab)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Oak, spruce, Acacia, dark oak, and jungle logs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">All log tops</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Oak, spruce, acacia, dark oak, jungle, and birch leaves</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Painting back</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This pack should be compatible with older versions of MC.</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/894050782004006962/1115117198806106122/timberhaus.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1184\" height=\"633\" /></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
